the%20higher%20command's%20objectives%20that%20they're%20giving%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Capt.%20Marek%2C%20a%20Polish%20passive%20controller%20who%20works%20with%20the%20AWACS'%20advanced%20sensors%2C%20said%20of%20the%20E-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNATO%20is%20planning%20to%20change%20the%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20this%20process%20takes%20time%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20our%20maintainers%2C%20our%20logistics%2C%20are%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20keep%20these%20jets%20in%20that%20perfect%20status.%20And%20I%20have%20no%20doubts%20that%20it%20will%20still%20be%20an%20operational%20jet%20for%20many%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-e-3-sentry-aircraft-old-but-still-surveillance-workhorse-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753716791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688772f23d5881a51c1e145e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-e-3-sentry-aircraft-old-but-still-surveillance-workhorse-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Business%20Insider%20flew%20aboard%20the%20decades-old%20aircraft%20during%20a%20recent%20surveillance%20mission.%20NATO%20plans%20to%20replace%20the%20E-3%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-e-3-sentry-aircraft-old-but-still-surveillance-workhorse-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Rick%20and%20Morty%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Phineas%20and%20Ferb%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Ghosts%E2%80%99%20Casts%20and%20More%20Join%20Variety%E2%80%99s%20Comic-Con%20Studio%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753716722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2F0C3A1519.jpg%3Fw%3D10