%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESolar%20dryers%20introduced%20under%20JH-RESET%20helped%20farmers%20cut%20crop%20losses%20and%20boost%20tomato%20profits%20by%2030%20to%2040%20percent%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20like%20Abdul%20from%20coal%20mining-intensive%20districts%2C%20such%20as%20Latehar%2C%20are%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20State%20Roadmap%20for%20Ecological%20and%20Sustainable%20Energy%20Transformation%20(JH-RESET)%20Project%2C%20a%20Swaniti%20Initiative-led%20project%20supported%20by%20the%20State%20government%20that%20began%20less%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Swaniti%20Initiative%20is%20a%20non-profit%20headquartered%20in%20Delhi%20that%20partners%20with%20State%20governments%20to%20improve%20the%20delivery%20of%20public%20services.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAimed%20at%20driving%20a%20sustainable%20energy%20transition%20in%20coal%20mining-affected%20districts%2C%20this%20project%20is%20helping%20smallholder%20farmers%20in%2012%20mining%20districts%20transition%20from%20low-value%20agriculture%20to%20high-value%20horticulture%2C%20addressing%20their%20supply%20chain%20and%20market%20access%20issues%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20access%20to%20solar-powered%20dryers%2C%20cold%20storage%20units%2C%20and%20pump%20sets.%20By%20deploying%20solar%20dryers%2C%20for%20example%2C%20tomato%20farmers%20in%20some%20of%20the%20best-performing%20districts%20saw%20a%2030-40%25%20rise%20in%20their%20monthly%20incomes%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclimate.swaniti.com%2Fhome%2Fprograms%2Fjharkhand%2F%5C%22%3E%20Swaniti%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20project%20aims%20to%20leverage%20existing%20employment%20exchanges%20for%20former%20mine%20workers%20and%20assist%20them%20in%20finding%20job%20opportunities%20in%20solar%20manufacturing%20and%20assembly%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20eco-tourism%2C%20and%20pisciculture.%20Given%20the%20expected%20closure%20of%20coal%20mines%