ebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSolar-Cold-Storage_11zon-1753711534.jpg%201600w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477360%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20dryers%20to%20cold%20storage%20units%2C%20solar%20tech%20is%20enabling%20Jharkhand%20farmers%20to%20move%20to%20high-value%20horticulture.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202015%2C%20parliamentarians%20from%20a%20few%20coal-mining%20districts%20in%20Jharkhand%20approached%20the%20%3Cstrong%3ESwaniti%20Initiative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20Delhi-based%20non-profit%20that%20partners%20with%20State%20governments%20to%20improve%20public%20service%20delivery.%20The%20MPs%20were%20keen%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20%3Cstrong%3EDistrict%20Mineral%20Foundation%20Trust%20(DMFT)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20funds%E2%80%94intended%20for%20welfare%20and%20development%20in%20mining-affected%20areas%E2%80%94were%20used%20in%20alignment%20with%20community%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20the%20DMFT%20is%20a%20public%20trust%20that%20channels%20funds%20towards%20developmental%20and%20welfare%20schemes%20in%20districts%20impacted%20by%20mining%20activity.%20The%20parliamentarians%2C%20responding%20to%20feedback%20from%20local%20leaders%2C%20wanted%20to%20deploy%20these%20funds%20more%20efficiently%20and%20with%20greater%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20initial%20conversations%2C%20we%20started%20testing%20out%20the%20waters%20by%20walking%20through%20district%20administrations%20overseeing%20these%20DMFT%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20%3Cstrong%3ERwitwika%20Bhattacharya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Swaniti%20Initiative%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20some%20champion%20bureaucrats%20at%20the%20time%20who%20really%20wanted%20to%20deploy%20their%20resources%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20aligned%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20communities%20they%20were%20serving.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swaniti%20began%20by%20working%20with%20local%20leaders%20and%20officials%20to%20align%20DMFT%20funds%20with%20community%20priorities.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1753711806-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477375%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESwaniti%20began%20by%20working%20with%20local%20leaders%20and%20officials%20to%20align%20DMFT%20funds%20with%20community%20priorities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20began%20with%20pilot%20programmes%20in%20%3Cstrong%3ERamgarh%20and%20Bokaro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20districts%20led%20by%20progressive%20district%20magistrates%20%3Cstrong%3EB%20Rajeshwari%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ERai%20Mahimapat%20Ray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(both%202011%20batch%20IAS%20officers).%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20focussed%20on%20figuring%20out%20what%20their%20communities%20needed%20and%20finding%20more%20sustainable%20economic%20opportunities%20for%20them%20aligned%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20(SDG