%22%3EDesigning%20a%20grounded%20training%20model%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Gaurav%20Bhattacharya%20of%20Swaniti%20explains%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20designed%20the%20curriculum%20for%20this%20training%20programme%20in%20consultation%20with%20agricultural%20scientists%20at%20the%20university.%20The%20demonstrations%20were%20done%20with%20experts%20from%20the%20KVKs.%20Few%20farmers%20were%20even%20brought%20to%20the%20university%20for%20some%20residential%20training.%20Given%20that%20we%20are%20a%20philanthropic%20foundation%2C%20we%20could%20only%20work%20on%20designing%20the%20curriculum.%20It%20was%20only%20KVKs%20that%20had%20the%20requisite%20network%20and%20resources%20to%20implement%20these%20training%20programmes.%20The%20university%20played%20the%20role%20of%20overseeing%20this%20programme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22PM-KUSUM-linked%20solar%20pumps%20became%20a%20lifeline%20for%20Jharkhand%20farmers%2C%20reducing%20costs%20and%20saving%20energy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FPM-Kusum-1_11zon-1753713026-4