0credits%2C%20and%20solar-powered%20irrigation%20benefits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20awareness%20and%20application%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAshok%20Samrat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20District%20Agriculture%20Officer%2C%20Chatra%2C%20reflects%20on%20the%20tangible%20outcomes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20district%2C%20farmers%20are%20engaged%20in%20the%20cultivation%20of%20tomatoes%2C%20cabbage%2C%20brinjal%2C%20and%20chillies.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20these%20farmers%20faced%20numerous%20challenges%20in%20cultivating%20these%20crops.%20Under%20the%20PM-KUSUM%20scheme%2C%20and%20with%20assistance%20from%20JREDA%20(Jharkhand%20Renewable%20Energy%20Development%20Agency)%2C%20we%20connected%20about%20300%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20farmer%20received%20a%20solar%20pump%20to%20irrigate%20their%20land%20thanks%20to%20the%20contributions%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%2C%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20and%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative.%20Initially%2C%20farmers%20neither%20had%20information%20about%20the%20scheme%20nor%20knew%20how%20to%20deploy%20solar%20pumps.%20However%2C%20farmers%20attended%20virtual%20training%20sessions%20organised%20by%20the%20agriculture%20department%2C%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20and%20the%20Swaniti%20Initiative%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20scheme%20and%20technology.%20Thanks%20to%20growing%20awareness%20of%20the%20scheme%20and%20technology%2C%20300%20farmers%20applied%2C%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20reviewed%20their%20applications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20few%20months%2C%20the%20solar%20pumps%20were%20installed.%20The%20response%2C%20according%20to%20Ashok%2C%20was%20swift%20and%20enthusiastic%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20are%20seeing%20that%20the%20farmers%20are%20very%20eager%20and%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this%20scheme.%20Using%20solar%20pump%20sets%2C