announced%20EU-US%20trade%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAviation's%20global%20supply%20chain%20and%20international%20reach%20mean%20tariffs%20would%20be%20particularly%20painful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAirlines%20and%20planemakers%20have%20spent%20months%20preparing%20workarounds%20in%20the%20event%20of%20tariffs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-eu-reach-trade-deal-ahead-of-tariff-deadline-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEU-US%20trade%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20a%20significant%20win%20for%20aviation%20after%20months%20of%20fears%20that%20the%20industry%20would%20face%20punishing%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20April's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20announcement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-are-set-to-make-your-next-flight-more-expensive-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%20initially%20imposed%20a%2020%25%20tariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20all%20exports%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%20Since%20negotiations%20have%20only%20seen%20that%20lowered%20to%2015%25%2C%20the%20deal%20is%20largely%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20win%20for%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20European%20companies%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbus-avoiding-trump-tariffs-sending-us-planes-to-other-countries-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAirbus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20still%20have%20reason%20to%20be%20cheerful%20because%20aircraft%20and%20their%20components%20are%20facing%20zero%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20aviation%20industry%20has%20faced%20a%20nervous%20few%20months%20of%20waiting%2C%20given%20its%20reliance%20on%20a%20highly%20complex%20and%20global%20supply%20chain%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0already%20under%20huge%20strain%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimism%20was%20already%20boosted%20at%20last%20month's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-air-show-aviation-boeing-airbus-reasons-to-be-cheerful-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParis%20Air%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20Transportation%20Secretary%20Sean%20Duffy%20said%20he%20favoured%20returning%20to%20a%20zero-tariff%20agreement%20from%201979%2C%20in%20line%20with%20much%20of%20the%20industry's%20top%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20planemakers%20and%20airlines%20have%20been%20devising%20creative%20ways%20to%20avoid%20Trump's%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-delta-ryanair-reject-planes-trump-tariffs-raise-prices-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDelta%20Air%20Lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20deployed%20a%20similar%20tactic%20from%20a%20past%20US-EU%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20airline%20had%20an%20Airbus%20plane%20delivered%20to%20Japan%20instead%20of%20the%20US.%20So%20long%20as%20the%20jet%20was%20only%20used%20for%20international%20flights%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20officially%20imported%20to%20the%20US%2C%20so%20there%20would%20be%20no%20tariffs%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Irish%20budget%20airline%20Ryanair%2C%20Europe's%20biggest%20carrier%20by%20passengers%2C%20was%20also%20preparing%20ways%20to%20limit%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Michael%20O'Leary%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call%20last%20week%20that%2C%20even%20though%20its%20deals%20with%20Boeing%20made%20the%20planemaker%20responsible%20for%20paying%20fees%2C%20the%20airline%20was%20willing%20to%20help%20find%20ways%20around%20it.%20He%20suggested%20registering%20planes%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20which%20also%20faces%20no%20aviation%20tariffs%2C%20or%20even%20delaying%20some%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20concerns%20aren't%20over%20for%20everyone%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20reaching%20a%20deal%20makes%20the%20future%20of%20the%20economy%20more%20predictable%2C%20many%20companies%20are%20expected%20to%20pass%20the%20costs%20of%20tariffs%20onto%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20coul