id.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20hope%20that%20if%20all%20of%20retail%20and%20all%20institutional%20investors%20truly%20believe%20in%20this%20%2482%20story%2C%20my%20hope%20is%20they%20zero%20in%20with%20like%2C%20the%20Death%20Star%20on%20this%20planet%2C%20and%20just%20buy%20and%20hold%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20believed%20investors%20could%20stage%20a%20rally%20similar%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-history-demise-cisco-sun-microsystems-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECisco's%3C%2Fa%3E%20meteoric%20rise%20during%20the%20dot-com%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20he%20emphasized%20that%20he's%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20people%20saying%20he%20sparked%20the%20meme%20stock%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20some%20grifter%20or%20flipper%2C%20no.%20I'm%20in%20this%20for%20the%20long%20run.%20I'm%20not%20here%20to%20pump%20up%20a%20stock%20and%20jump%20out%20of%20it.%20I've%20never%20done%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopendoor-stock-price-meme-stocks-rally-eric-jackson-emj-capital-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753695001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688789c385e81483682ec413%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopendoor-stock-price-meme-stocks-rally-eric-jackson-emj-capital-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Eric%20Jackson%2C%20who%20spotted%20potential%20in%20Carvana%20in%202022%2C%20has%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20a%20new%20%26quot%3B100-bagger.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopendoor-stock-price-meme-stocks-rally-eric-jackson-emj-capital-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Behind%20Michael%20Gelband%20and%20%2411%20billion%20hedge%20fund%20ExodusPoint's%20strong%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225526%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wall%20Street%20bull%20statue%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6706d22b3f2165d716df9f1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWall%20Street%20bull%3Cp%3ERobert%20Nickelsberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMichael%20Gelband's%20ExodusPoint%20is%20atop%20the%20leaderboard%20midway%20through%202025%2C%20besting%20peers%20like%20Millennium.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%2411%20billion%20firm%20was%20the%20biggest%20launch%20in%20industry%20history%2C%20starting%20with%20more%20than%20%248%20billion%20in%202018.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20manager%20has%20leaned%20on%20its%20fixed-income%20expertise%20to%20drive%20strong%20returns%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20sky-high%20expectations%20for%20the%20ExodusPoint%20Capital%20Management%20when%20it%20launched%207%20years%20ago.%20It's%20starting%20to%20meet%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2411%20billion%20firm%20was%20the%20largest%20launch%20in%20industry%20history%20in%202018%20thanks%20to%20the%20stellar%20track%20record%20of%20cofounder%20Michael%20Gelband%2C%20who%20previously%20led%20Millennium's%20fixed-income%20division.%20He%20told%20former%20colleagues%20that%20his%20unit%20generated%20%247%20billion%20in%20trading%20revenue%20in%20his%20eight%20years%20at%20Izzy%20Englander's%20firm%2C%20and%20hedge%20fund%20backers%20rushed%20to%20invest%20in%20his%20new%20firm%2C%20which%20started%20trading%20with%20a%20record%20%248.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20putting%20all%20of%20the%20capital%20to%20work%2C%20hiring%20scores%20of%20investors%2C%20setting%20up%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20finding%20the%20right%20leadership%20took%20time.%20The%20firm%2C%20which%20was%20also%20cofounded%20by%20former%20Millennium%20equities%20executive%20Hyung%20Lee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexoduspoint-capital-management-hedge-fund-michael-gelband-performance-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20a%20relative%20disappointment%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20start%2C%20with%20the%20difficult%20reality%20of%20being%20compared%20to%20funds%20like%20the%20cofounders'%20former%20employer%20and%20Ken%20Griffin's%20Citadel%20from%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20little%20over%20seven%20years%20after%20the%20manager%20first%20began%20trading%2C%20the%20New%20York-based%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjune-hedge-fund-performance-citadel-balyasny-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20outperformed%20its%20peers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202025%20and%20over%20the%20last%2012%20months.%20The%20manager%20is%20up%20more%20than%209%25%20after%20a%201.8%25%20June%20gain.%20Since%20the%20start%20of%20July%202024%2C%20ExodusPoint%20has%20returned%20more%20than%2018%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FxHtBi%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FxHtBi%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20firm's%20operations%20pointed%20to%20several%20factors%20as%20to%20why.%20This%20person%20is%20not%20permitted%20to%20speak%20publicly%20about%20the%20manager's%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20roller%20coaster%20equities%20market%2C%20ExodusPoint%20has%20benefited%20from%20its%20fixed-income%20lean.%20Roughly%2075%25%20of%20the%20firm's%20risk%20is%20in%20fixed-income%20books%2C%20the%20person%20close%20to%20the%20firm%20said%2C%20which%20is%20Gelband's%20specialty%2C%20though%20the%20cofounder%20does%20not%20manage%20money%20himself.%20Jon%20Hoffman%2C%20a%20former%20Lehman%20Brothers%20trader%20who%20worked%20with%20Gelband%20at%20the%20bank%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20firm's%20best-known%20portfolio%20managers%20with%20his%20basis-trade%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGelband%20is%20now%20the%20sole%20chief%20investment%20officer%20after%20Lee%20stepped%20down%20in%202024%20(the%20cofounder%2C%20who%20had%20relocated%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20is%20currently%20a%20senior%20advisor).%20The%20firm%20made%20several%20hires%20in%202023%20who%20have%20led%20units%20that%20were%20previously%20under%20Lee's%20purview%2C%20such%20as%20Adam%20Galeon%20and%20Michael%20Lapsa%2C%20who%20run%20long-short%20equities%20and%20systematic%20strategies%2C%20respectively.%20Peter%20McConnon%2C%20once%20the%20head%20of%20London%20macro%20for%20Balyasny%2C%20was%20also%20brought%20in%20during%20this%20time%20as%20a%20senior%20managing%20director%20of%20fixed%20income%20and%20macro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20members%20of%20the%20original%20team%20such%20as%20Lee%20and%20former%20chief%20risk%20officer%20Dev%20Joneja%20have%20moved%20into%20advisory%20roles%2C%20Garrett%20Berg%2C%20a%20day-one%20employee%20who%20has%20since%20been%20promoted%20to%20president%20and%20COO%2C%20and%20Kunal%20Kumar%2C%20a%20former%20Balyasny%20executive%20who%20joined%20in%202023%20and%20is%20now%20chief%20risk%20officer%2C%20have%20been%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20progress%20on%20both%20the%20investment%20and%20non-investment%20sides%20of%20the%20business%2C%20this%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20adopted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexoduspoint-multistrategy-hedge-funds-lower-fees-adopt-cash-hurdle-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20cash%20hurdle%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20performance%20fees%20last%20year%2C%20meaning%20ExodusPoint%20only%20collects%20performance%20fees%20when%20it%20returns%20more%