%2FMinimalist-Square-Photo-Instagram-Post-3_11zon-1753498622-600x600.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMinimalist-Square-Photo-Instagram-Post-3_11zon-1753498622-400x400.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMinimalist-Square-Photo-Instagram-Post-3_11zon-1753498622-200x200.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMinimalist-Square-Photo-Instagram-Post-3_11zon-1753498622-96x96.jpg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FMinimalist-Square-Photo-Instagram-Post-3_11zon-1753498622.jpg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476555%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBefore%20Everest%2C%20Aritra%20trained%20by%20summiting%20Lobuche%20East%20(6%2C119%20m)%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20extreme%20altitude.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20plans%20to%20conduct%20workshops%20in%20schools%20and%20colleges%20in%20Tripura%20to%20promote%20fitness%2C%20endurance%20sports%2C%20and%20mental%20strength.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20young%20people%E2%80%99s%20confidence.%20They%20have%20the%20fire.%20They%20just%20need%20someone%20to%20show%20them%20the%20path.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Arjun%20beautifully%20summarizes%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20to%20describe%20Aritra%E2%80%99s%20expedition%20in%20a%20metaphor%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20say%20he%20was%20like%20a%20flame%20that%20learned%20to%20burn%20brighter%20in%20the%20thin%20air.%20Everest%20strips%20you%20to%20your%20core.%20Most%20flicker%20out.%20But%20Aritra%20thrived.%20The%20higher%20the%20stakes%2C%20the%20stronger%20his%20resolve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20story%20that%20is%20just%20starting%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20would%20retire%20from%20adventure%20after%20such%20a%20feat%2C%20Aritra%20is%20already%20dreaming%20up%20his%20next%20challenge%2C%20something%20even%20more%20accessible%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20this%20to%20be%20about%20just%20me.%20I%20want%20to%20build%20a%20community%20of%20endurance%20athletes%20from%20the%20Northeast%2C%20from%20regular%20working%20backgrounds.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20million%20followers%20or%20big%20sponsors.%20You%20just%20need%20to%20start.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20between%20stand-up%20meetings%20and%20sprint%20planning%20sessions%2C%20Aritra%20is%20just%20another%20guy%20at%20his%20desk.%20But%20in%20his%20heart%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20still%20on%20the%20trail%2C%20carrying%20the%20flag%20of%20India%20to%20new%20heights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Ashirbani%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20might%20be%20a%20software%20engineer%20by%20profession%2C%20but%20in%20spirit%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20an%20explorer.%20And%20this%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1753500600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img_11zon-1753497703.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D476536%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aritra%20Roy%2C%20a%20software%20engineer%20from%20Tripura%2C%20completed%20a%20triathlon%20to%20Mount%20Everest%20%E2%80%94%20cycling%20across%20states%2C%20summiting%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20peak%2C%20and%20running%20a%20marathon%20%E2%80%94%20while%20managing%20his%20corporate%20job%20at%20TCS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F476536%2Ftechie-mountaineer-everest-aritra-roy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20Sighting%20in%20Kargil%3A%20Adorable%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20Cub%20Follows%20Its%20Mother%20Through%20the%20Wild%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3C